    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/f2d92fb7e9f354744bf35fcd2570353e.poster.avif?t=1761572527\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/f2d92fb7e9f354744bf35fcd2570353e.webm?t=1761572527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/f2d92fb7e9f354744bf35fcd2570353e.mp4?t=1761572527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For hundreds of years, the elders have spoken of a unique city, made entirely of gold, hidden from the world for 500 years; according to legend, there is only one map, which was separated into parts and hidden all over the world. This is how hundreds of brave men and women began their search, braving the unknown, in the fantastic world of Sea of Brave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sea of Brave Beast Island is a turn-based, tactical deck-building roguelike game for one player. Join Aidan on his perilous adventure on Benryu Island, defeating Captain Kingg's minions to uncover his secrets. Create a unique deck by discovering new cards, allies, or improving your deck through each battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/29de63e9adf71cbe44dd106dba72c0cb.avif?t=1761572527\" width=512 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characteristics:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tDynamic deck building: Discover a wide variety of cards to combine in your various battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tStrategic Battles: Carefully choose your cards each turn, boosting your attacks or fiercely defending your position to defeat the enemy. Don't let them capture you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tMaximize Synergies: Combine cards to boost your defense and attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tUnique game generation: Island maps change with every attempt as each map in each chapter is randomly generated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tFind Allies: Discover and find allies in your adventure, unlocking their unique cards that you can use in your battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tAccessories: Enhance your games with a wide variety of accessories to boost your skills with extraordinary effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/eec84c769ef1ff8b9879e754531294b3.poster.avif?t=1761572527\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/eec84c769ef1ff8b9879e754531294b3.webm?t=1761572527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/eec84c769ef1ff8b9879e754531294b3.mp4?t=1761572527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/5c5f8f5b5393df6e5665da3b00c8205e.poster.avif?t=1761572527\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/5c5f8f5b5393df6e5665da3b00c8205e.webm?t=1761572527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006480/extras/5c5f8f5b5393df6e5665da3b00c8205e.mp4?t=1761572527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
